dc_title_s: Laurie and Whittle's new chart of the Indian and Pacific Oceans between the Cape of Good Hope, New Holland and Japan:
dc_description_s: Scale approximately 1:17 000 000. Map of Indian and Pacific Oceans showing explorers' tracks. Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridian: London. Includes 3 views and notes. Australia named "New Holland or Terra Australis." Contents: Insets: Anson's road at the west end of Tinian -- Isle of Norfolk or New Norfolk. 1 map : color ; 75 x 109 cm
dc_publisher_sm: R. Laurie & J. Whittle Fleet Street
